            </p>
            <p><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><img src="img/button.gif" width="20" height="14"> 
              <font color="#FF9900">GUILD INVITE POLICY </font><br>
              <img src="img/button.gif" width="20" height="14"> </font><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="1">updated</font><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"> 
              : June 15th 2001</font></p>
            <p><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><img src="img/button.gif" width="20" height="14"> 
              <font color="#FF9900">Information</font></font></p>
            <p><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">So, 
              you`re interested in becoming a member of Eternus Astralis are you?</font></p>
            <p><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">Eternus 
              Astralis is always looking for exceptional individuals who can bring 
              something special to our guild. </font></p>
            <p><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">We 
              are a raiding guild and thus, we spend the majority of our time 
              raiding alot. Therefor, <i>we are not interested in casual gamers</i>. 
              If you have the time to dedicate to raiding and the eagerness to 
              do new and fun things, then Eternus Astralis is a good pick. Eternus 
              Astralis raids on average between 3 and 4 days a week, the other 
              3 and 4 days are spent however our members like. However, if you 
              do not have the time to spend during our 3-4 days of mandatory raid 
              days, then unfortunately Eternus Astralis is not the guild for you.</font></p>
            <p><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">We 
              currently have a preference for the following classes : </font></p>
